qDef.qDef:
=Pick
    (
        $(v_Switch_Option_Expansion)
        
        ,$(v_Customers_Totaly_New_Net_Weight)/1000
        ,$(v_WinBack_MQP_NetSalesKG_YTD)/1000
        ,$(v_Periodic_WinBack_MT)
        ,$(v_WinBack_NetSalesKG_YTD)/1000
        ,( $(v_Customers_Totaly_New_Net_Weight) + $(v_WinBack_MQP_NetSalesKG_YTD) +($(v_Periodic_WinBack_MT)*1000) +$(v_WinBack_NetSalesKG_YTD))/1000
        ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
        ,$(v_WinBack_MQP_NetSalesKG_YTD)/1000 + $(v_WinBack_NetSalesKG_YTD)/1000
     )

Pick
    (
       $(v_Switch_Option_Expansion)
       
        ,$(v_Customers_Totaly_New_Net_Sales)/1000
        ,$(v_WinBack_MQP_NetSales_YTD)/1000
        ,$(v_Periodic_Winback_Sales)/1000
         ,$(v_WinBack_NetSales_YTD)/1000
 		, ($(v_Customers_Totaly_New_Net_Sales) + $(v_WinBack_MQP_NetSales_YTD) + $(v_Periodic_Winback_Sales) +$(v_WinBack_NetSales_YTD))/1000
        , (Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate]))/1000
         ,$(v_WinBack_MQP_NetSales_YTD)/1000  +   $(v_WinBack_NetSales_YTD)/1000
     )

Pick
    (
       $(v_Switch_Option_Expansion)
       
        ,$(v_Customers_Totaly_New_COP)/1000
        ,$(v_WinBack_MQP_COP_YTD)/1000
        ,$(v_Periodic_WinBack_COP)/1000
         ,$(v_WinBack_COP_YTD)/1000
 		, ($(v_Customers_Totaly_New_COP) + $(v_WinBack_MQP_COP_YTD) + $(v_Periodic_WinBack_COP) +$(v_WinBack_COP_YTD))/1000
        , (Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} ([Invoice Amount USD]-[Invoice Cost USD])*[Currency Average Rate]))/1000
        ,$(v_WinBack_MQP_COP_YTD)/1000 + $(v_WinBack_COP_YTD)/1000
     )

Num(
Pick
    (
      $(v_Switch_Option_Expansion)
      
        ,'0'
        , $(v_WinBack_MQP_Budget_KG_YTD)/1000
        ,$(v_Periodic_Winback_Budget_MT)
        , ($(v_WinBack_Budget_KG_YTD))/1000
        , ( $(v_Customers_Totaly_New_Net_Weight) + $(v_WinBack_MQP_NetSalesKG_YTD) +($(v_Periodic_WinBack_MT)*1000) +$(v_WinBack_NetSalesKG_YTD)) / 
          (Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT]) *1000)
        ,  (Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget MT]))
         , $(v_WinBack_MQP_Budget_KG_YTD)/1000  +  ($(v_WinBack_Budget_KG_YTD))/1000
     
     )
     
   ,
    Text
    (
      Pick
      (
       $(v_Switch_Option_Expansion)
          , '#,##0'
          ,  '#,##0'
          ,  '#,##0'
          , '#,##0'
          , '0.00%'
          , '#,##0'
          ,  '#,##0'
         )
   )
   , '.' , ',' )

Num(
Pick
    (
     $(v_Switch_Option_Expansion)
        ,'0'
        ,($(v_WinBack_MQP_Budget_NetSales_YTD))/1000
        ,($(v_Periodic_Winback_Budget_Sales))/1000
        ,($(v_WinBack_Budget_NetSales_YTD))/1000
        ,(($(v_Customers_Totaly_New_Net_Sales) + $(v_WinBack_MQP_NetSales_YTD) + $(v_Periodic_Winback_Sales) +$(v_WinBack_NetSales_YTD)) / 
        ( Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])))
        
        ,   Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
            /1000
            
         ,($(v_WinBack_MQP_Budget_NetSales_YTD))/1000   + ($(v_WinBack_Budget_NetSales_YTD))/1000
            
     )
     
   ,
    Text
    (
      Pick
      (
       $(v_Switch_Option_Expansion)
          , '#,##0'
          ,  '#,##0'
          ,  '#,##0'
          , '#,##0'
          , '0.00%'
          , '#,##0'
           , '#,##0'
         )
   )
   , '.' , ',' )

Num(

        ,(($(v_Customers_Totaly_New_COP) + $(v_WinBack_MQP_COP_YTD) + $(v_Periodic_WinBack_COP) +$(v_WinBack_COP_YTD)) / 
        ( Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} ([Invoice Amount USD]-[Invoice Cost USD])*[Currency Average Rate])))
        
        ,   Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} ([Budget Amount USD]-[Budget Cost USD])*[Currency Average Rate])
            /1000
     
         ,($(v_WinBack_MQP_Budget_COP_YTD))/1000
     	    + ($(v_WinBack_Budget_COP_YTD))/1000
     )
     
   ,
    Text
    (
      Pick
      (
       $(v_Switch_Option_Expansion)
          , '#,##0'
          ,  '#,##0'
          ,  '#,##0'
          , '#,##0'
          , '0.00%'
          , '#,##0'
             , '#,##0'
         )
